headline: Public Storage Prices Public Offering of Euro-Denominated Senior Notes
summary: GLENDALE, Calif., September 26, 2025--Public Storage (NYSE:PSA, the "Company") announced today that the Company’s subsidiary, Public Storage Operating Company ("PSOC"), has priced a public offering of €425 million aggregate principal amount of senior notes due 2034 (the "Notes"). The Notes will be guaranteed by the Company.
